LangleyHostNotConfiguredAlarm.label="Trusted Infrastructure 主机 Not 已配置 警报"
LangleyHostNotConfiguredAlarm.summary="警报 to notify that an ESX 主机, member of Trust Authority 集群 or Trusted 集群, 不 已配置."
