TaHostAttestStatusAlarm.summary="Default 警报 which indicates that a Trusted 主机 has 失败 at测试ation 使用 已配置 Trust Authority at测试ation 服务(s)."
TaStsCertificatesChangeAlarm.label="STS 证书s 更改 警报"
TaStsCertificatesChangeAlarm.summary="STS 证书s have 已更改. Trust authority 集群 needs to be 已重新配置. Please execute step '导入 the Trusted 主机 信息 到 Trust Authority 集群' from 'vSphere Trust Authority manual'."
