KeyProviderNotBackedUpAlarm.summary="警报 to indicate that one or more 键 provIDErs require 备份."

### Host Config Encryption Recovery Key Alarm
HostTpmConfigEncryptionAlarm.label="TPM 加密 Rec超过y 键 备份 警报"
HostTpmConfigEncryptionAlarm.summary="Default 警报 which indicates that 主机 配置 is TPM encrypted. Rec超过y 键 备份 may be performed in order to 恢复 主机 配置 on TPM failure. https://knowledge.broadcom.com/external/article/323401"

### Memory mode alarms
HostMemoryModeHighActiveDRAMAlarm.label="主机 内存 Mode High 活动 DRAM 使用率"
HostMemoryModeHighActiveDRAMAlarm.summary="The 警报 is 触发 when the 活动 内存 of all 虚拟机s 在 主机 exceeds the required DRAM occupancy when the 主机 is 已配置 in 内存 Mode. Please consIDEr 正在迁移 some 虚拟机s to other 主机s."

VmHighPMemB和widthAlarm.label="虚拟机 High PMem 带宽 使用率"
VmHighPMemB和widthAlarm.summary="The 警报 is 触发 when the '主机 内存 Mode High 活动 DRAM' condition is satisfied 和 this 虚拟机's PMem 带宽 is greater than the required DRAM 带宽. Please consIDEr 正在迁移 this 虚拟机 to another 主机."

### Tiering Memory alarms
TieredHostHighActiveDRAMAlarm.label="Tiered 主机 High 活动 DRAM 内存 使用率"
TieredHostHighActiveDRAMAlarm.summary="The 警报 is 触发 when the 活动 内存 of all 虚拟机s 在 主机 exceeds the required DRAM occupancy when the 主机 is 已配置 as tiered 主机. Please consIDEr 正在迁移 some 虚拟机s to other 主机s."

TieredVmHighTier1B和widthAlarm.label="虚拟机 Tier 1 High 带宽 使用率"
TieredVmHighTier1B和widthAlarm.summary="The 警报 is 触发 after 'Tiered 主机 High 活动 DRAM 内存 使用率' 警报 is raised 和 this 虚拟机's tier 1 带宽 is higher than expected. Please consIDEr 正在迁移 this 虚拟机 to another 主机."

